# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok vietnam has announced an #.#-billion-dollar economic and defense development plan for a string of islands along its resource-rich coastline , as a broader sovereignty dispute simmers with china .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Vietnam"))
      :ARG1 (p / plan-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (d / develop-02
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (e / economy)
                        :op2 (d2 / defend-01)))
            :ARG3 (m / multiple
                  :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                        :quant 1000000000
                        :unit (d3 / dollar)))
            :beneficiary (ii / island
                  :quant (s / string)
                  :location (a3 / along
                        :op1 (c2 / coastline
                              :poss c
                              :mod (r / rich
                                    :mod (r2 / resource))))))
      :time (s2 / simmer-01
            :ARG1 (d4 / dispute-01
                  :ARG2 (s3 / sovereignty)
                  :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                        :ARG2 (b / broad-02
                              :ARG1 d4)
                        :ARG3 (m3 / more)))
            :ARG2 (c3 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "China"))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok fiji sevens player marika vunibaka has been suspended for ## weeks for his part in a brawl with new zealand players during a world series tournament in chile last week .
# ::alignments
(s / suspend-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Marika"
                  :op2 "Vunibaka")
            :ARG0-of (p2 / play-01
                  :ARG1 (g / game
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Fiji"
                              :op2 "7s"))))
      :duration (m / multiple
            :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (w / week)))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (b / brawl-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (p4 / play-01
                              :ARG1 (g2 / game
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "New"
                                          :op2 "Gealand"))))
                  :time (t2 / tournament
                        :mod (s2 / series
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "World"
                                    :op2 "Series"))
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Chile"))
                        :time (w2 / week
                              :mod (l / last))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok president ricardo maduro said tuesday he will declare a state of alert against the possible arrival of sars in this central american country .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Ricardo"
                  :op2 "Maduro")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (d / declare-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (s2 / state
                  :mod (a / alert-01))
            :ARG2 (a2 / arrive-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Sars")))
            :ARG4 (c2 / country
                  :location (w / world-region
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Central"
                              :op2 "America"))
                  :mod (t / this))
            :ARG1-of (p3 / possible-01))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok police are investigating a letter that threatened more attacks on northeastern british columbia 's natural gas facilities , where a series of pipelines have been bombed in the last two years .
# ::alignments
(ii / investigate-01
      :ARG0 (p / police)
      :ARG1 (l / letter
            :ARG0-of (t / threaten-01
                  :ARG1 (a / attack-01
                        :ARG1 (f / facility
                              :mod (g / gas
                                    :ARG1-of (n / natural-03))
                              :location (n2 / northeast
                                    :part-of (c / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Britain")))
                              :location-of (b / bomb-01
                                    :ARG1 (p2 / pipeline
                                          :quant (s / series))
                                    :time (b2 / before
                                          :op1 (n4 / now)
                                          :duration (t2 / temporal-quantity
                                                :quant 2
                                                :unit (y / year)))))
                        :mod (m / more)))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :op1 "Egypt")))
      :ARG1 (a2 / arrive-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Yossi"
                        :op2 "Beilin")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c2 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Israel"))
                        :ARG2 (m / minister
                              :topic (j / justice))
                        :time (f / former)))
            :ARG4 (h2 / here)
            :time (l / late
                  :op1 (d / date-entity
                        :dayperiod (n6 / night)
                        :mod (s2 / sunday)))
            :purpose (m2 / meet-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n7 / name
                              :op1 "Ahmed"
                              :op2 "Maher")
                        :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 c
                              :ARG2 (m3 / minister
                                    :topic (f2 / foreign))))
                  :ARG2 (t / tense-01
                        :location (w / world-region
                              :name (n8 / name
                                    :op1 "Mideast"))))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :mod (o / official)

                  :ARG1 (p / person

      :ARG1 (a2 / and
            :op1 (a3 / attend-02
                  :ARG0 (o3 / organization
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "Arab"
                              :op3 "Emirates"))
                  :ARG1 (a4 / and
                        :op1 (s / secure-02
                              :ARG1 (f / facility
                                    :ARG1-of (p2 / plan-01
                                          :ARG0 o3)
                                    :mod (n4 / nucleus)))
                        :op2 (s2 / safe-01
                              :ARG1 f))
                  :ARG1-of (h / high-02))
            :op2 (t / try-01
                  :ARG0 o3
                  :ARG1 (p3 / prevent-01
                        :ARG0 o3
                        :ARG1 (a5 / and
                              :op1 (e / emergency)
                              :op2 (c2 / crisis)
                              :mod (a6 / any)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok do n't try this at home , but experiments in mice indicate that inhaling carbon monoxide can save the animals ' lives after severe lung damage .
# ::alignments
(c / contrast-01
      :ARG1 (t / try-01
            :polarity -
            :mode imperative
            :ARG0 (y / you)
            :ARG1 (t2 / this)
            :location (h / home))
      :ARG2 (ii / indicate-01
            :ARG0 (e / experiment-01
                  :location (m / mouse))
            :ARG1 (p / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (s / save-02
                        :ARG0 (ii2 / inhale-01
                              :ARG1 (m2 / monoxide
                                    :mod (c2 / carbon)))
                        :ARG1 (l / life
                              :poss (a / animal))
                        :time (a2 / after
                              :op1 (d / damage-01
                                    :ARG1 (l2 / lung)
                                    :degree (s2 / severe)))))))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :mod (y / yankee)

            :mod (y2 / york))
      :ARG1 (c / chance-02
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Dwight"
                        :op2 "Gooden"))
            :mod (a / another
                  :mod (y3 / yet)))
      :ARG2 p2)

                              :ARG1-of (p / possible-01))))

                  :weekday (f / friday)))

            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (a4 / assert-02

# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (r / reject-01
            :ARG0 (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "China"))
            :ARG1 (c2 / claim-01
                  :ARG0 (p / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Lee"
                              :op2 "Teng-hui")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Taiwan"))
                              :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
                  :ARG1 (d / depend-01
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0 (ii / island
                              :poss p)))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday)))
      :op2 (c4 / call-03
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (s / start-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (t2 / talk-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (r2 / reunite-01
                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (m / mainland))))
            :ARG2 p))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Ludmilla"
                  :op2 "Ibrahim")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / commission
                        :mod (e / elect-01))
                  :ARG2 (c2 / chairwoman)))
      :ARG1 (w / win-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Alexander"
                        :op2 "Lukashenko")
                  :ARG0-of h
                  :ARG1 (c3 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Belarus"))
                  :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
      :ARG1 (a / approve-01
            :ARG1 p2
            :manner (m / margin
                  :mod (l / large)))
      :ARG3 (r / referendum
            :mod (c4 / controversy)
            :topic (ii / increase-01
                  :ARG1 (p4 / power
                        :poss p2)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

# ::id 1922 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok budget airline ryanair published its hostile takeover plans for irish rival aer lingus on monday -- and warned the carrier 's shareholders they stood to lose money if they did n't accept the offer .

      :op1 (p / publish-01
            :ARG0 (a2 / airline

                  :ARG0 a2
                  :ARG1 (t / take-over-12
                        :ARG0 a2

                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Aer"
                                    :op2 "Lingus")
                              :mod (c2 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Ireland"))

                                    :ARG1 a2)))
                  :mod (h / hostile))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday)))
      :op2 (w / warn-01
            :ARG0 a2
            :ARG1 (s / stand-08
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / hold-01
                              :ARG1 (s2 / share
                                    :poss (c3 / carrier))))
                  :ARG2 (l / lose-02
                        :ARG0 p3
                        :ARG1 (m2 / money)
                        :condition (a3 / accept-01
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG0 p3
                              :ARG1 (o / offer-01
                                    :ARG0 p3))))
            :ARG2 p3))
